ice providers\u2192 to product creators\u2192 to category leaders.Because writing code scales.But building products changes the world.The real question is\u2026When the mindset shifts,how fast could everything change? \ud83d\ude80Follow @sonanos.news if you want to stay ahead of where tech is really going.\". ", "large_image": "vUfXYnpLgqLNuqSI.png", "title": "Sonanos AI News on Instagram: \"Everyone talks about talent.But talent isn\u2019t the bottleneck.India produces millions of engineers.Some of the best in the world.Yet most global products still come from the same few countries.So what\u2019s missing?It\u2019s not skill.It\u2019s product thinking.Building for users, not just requirements.Taking risks, not just executing tasks.It\u2019s ecosystem.Access to capital.Mentors who\u2019ve done it before.A culture that rewards long-term bets, not short-term output.It\u2019s ownership mindset.From s"}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2041213196984279144", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZHcGFdB", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 294, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8540219, "raw_content": "", "author": "AslanFan", "created": 1775501093171, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "NecturusMaculosus", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZHcGFdB.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/overton_news/status/2041213196984279144", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Ever heard a head of CIA talk this way to POTUS?", "last_comment_created": 1775521925606, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "